  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6778 trading just below the GEX flip at 6783 in a PIN regime, dealers are positioned as stabilizers and should be providing buying support here given proximity to the massive +12.5B gamma wall at 6780. The recent GEX surge (73.7% in 1-min) indicates heavy options flow that's likely reinforcing dealer positioning as net long gamma sellers into strength. Key levels: 6780 resistance where dealers sell heavily, 6770 support where negative gamma creates amplified moves if breached, and 6783 flip strike that determines regime sustainability.\n\n**Bottom line:** expect the market to get pinned between 6770-6780 with choppy mean-reverting action.",
